All 6 features implemented and verified. Here's what changed:

**`app/auth.py`** — `require_api_key` now validates the `X-API-Key` header against `VALID_API_KEYS`. Returns the username on success, raises 401 if missing or invalid.

**`app/main.py`** — Four changes:

1. **`GET /tasks`** — Added optional query params `status`, `priority`, `assigned_to` for filtering (all combinable), plus `page` (default 1) and `page_size` (default 20) for pagination.

2. **`POST /tasks`** — New endpoint. Requires auth via `Depends(require_api_key)`. Validates `project_id` exists (404 if not). Auto-generates ID. Returns 201 with created task.

3. **`PUT /tasks/{task_id}`** — New endpoint. Requires auth. Partial update using `model_dump(exclude_unset=True)` so only provided fields are changed. Returns 404 if task not found.

4. **`DELETE /tasks/{task_id}`** — New endpoint. Requires auth. Removes and returns the task. Returns 404 if not found.

